    <subfield code="o">10</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">Throughout the paper we shall use the capital Greek letters Œ®(t, r) and Œ¶(t, r) to denote the time-dependent fields and the minuscules Greek letters œà(r</subfield>
  </datafield>
