  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="o">22</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">Defining œÜ ‚â° œà1 + b ¬∑ œà2, one obtains from Eqs. (18)-(19) the wave equation: ( d2 dr2 + œâ2 - ¬µ2 )œÜ - 8-6b r2 (œà1 + -4+6b 8-6b œà2) = 0. Demanding the equality -4+6b 8-6b = b, one obtains the quadratic equation 3b2 -b-2 = 0 for the coefficient b, whose solutions are given by Eq. (20). The decoupled wave equations are then given by ( d2 dr2 + œâ2 - ¬µ2 - 8-6b r2 )œÜ = 0, see Eqs. (21)-(22)</subfield>
