  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="o">23</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">Here the fields œà1, œà2, and œà3 respectively correspond to the functions rK, Œ∑1, and rG in Eqs. (38)-(40) of [5]</subfield>
